So I suppose what I am imagining is something like
```
query testsQuery {
  allTests(customArg: "1") {
    ...__RelayQueryFragment0pgs7aw
  }
}
fragment __RelayQueryFragment0pgs7aw on Test{custom_id,description, test_name, id}
```

